---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro'
---

<PageLayout
  title="Contact Me"
  subtitle="Nobody uses the phone any more. But drop me an email here and I'll get back to you."
  description="Email Wade to get in touch."
  featured_image="/images/site/contact.jpg"
>
  <div class="mb-8">
    <form method="post" action="https://smartforms.dev/submit/5fe8fa14b81854118fd3f8e6" class="space-y-6">
      <div>
        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-medium)] mb-2">Email Address *</label>
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your email address..." required
          class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:border-[var(--color-accent)] transition-colors" />
      </div>

      <div>
        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-medium)] mb-2">Name *</label>
        <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your name..." required
          class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:border-[var(--color-accent)] transition-colors" />
      </div>

      <div>
        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-medium)] mb-2">Message *</label>
        <textarea name="message" placeholder="Your message..." required rows="6"
          class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:border-[var(--color-accent)] transition-colors"></textarea>
      </div>

      <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="/thanks" />
      <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Email from wademinter.com" />
      <input type="text" name="_gotcha" style="display: none;" />

      <div>
        <button type="submit"
          class="px-8 py-3 bg-[var(--color-accent)] text-white font-semibold rounded-md hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity cursor-pointer">
          Send Email
        </button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>

  <p>I generally reply to emails in a day or two. You can also email me directly at <code>wade AT wademinter DOT com</code>.</p>
</PageLayout>
